    {
      "chinese": "這兩塊居住地區的水源和空氣到目前還没有被污染。這裡休閒農業區最適合栽培有機農作（無農藥和化學肥料），完全依靠土壤的地力栽培作物，因此，設置休閒農業應列為部落的重點計畫之一。",
      "ab": "Tona tosaay a kamaro’an, o cowa ho kamasokadi ko nanom ato fali. O matatodongay paloma to awaay ko sapaiyo ato sasiwtok, saheto o pakaseraay a maemin ko lalislisen to ’a’anipen, midoedo to no litengan a pinangan ko paliomah. Saka, mihalaka ko niyaro’ to pisalamaan a patireng to masafohokay a pala.",
      "order": "2",
      "sound": "https://dzywvpqnys6mw.cloudfront.net/files/2021/04/08/9c33ea7188cb0fc5d524f4ad1e8d8fc5.wav",
